<i>adverb</i>: 그때그때 [그때그때], 고때고때 [고때고때] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>그때그때 [그때그때]</dt><br>
<dd>according to circumstances; whenever</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 기회가 생길 때마다.</dd><br>
<dd>Whenever something happens or there is an opportunity.</dd><br>
<dt>고때고때 [고때고때]</dt><br>
<dd>whenever; according to circumstances</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 기회가 생길 때마다.</dd><br>
<dd>Whenever something happens or there is an opportunity; at every opportunity.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>